{"tid":869380,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門澤豐花園累減29%至393萬元沽出","createTime":"2018-10-20T09:51:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-20T14:52:35.000Z","uid":53484,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"df463170bce33eef31e8c1eacdedbc0ed30d180e","tid":869380,"uid":53484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T09:51:24.000Z","msg":"祥益地產分行主任李啟昌表示，居屋澤豐花園5座低層B室，實用面積462平方呎，原業主於今年9月放盤，叫價550萬元，及至近日以393萬元沽出，期間累減157萬元，幅度29%，以393萬元自由市場易手，實用面積呎價8,506元。買家為區內上車客。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屯門澤豐花園累減29%至393萬元沽出<br />\n<br />\n原業主於08年以85萬元自由市場購入，雖劈價沽貨，但帳面仍賺308萬元，物業10年升值3.6倍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2190034?r=cpstna\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2190034%3Fr%3Dcpstna&d=x4AIMnCd63fjn2p%2F6iqpFNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=a20d20f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2190034?r=cpstna</a>"},{"pid":"d0b11113e0e4c609105a2db0a4827036b6983f9a","tid":869380,"uid":88785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T09:52:03.000Z","msg":"唔計"},{"pid":"827560796fbc789b54cc520a132ec757d2f627bb","tid":869380,"uid":12609,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T09:54:54.000Z","msg":"低智小朋友：業主唔係等錢駛，做乜要平賣比你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4961d52aa4fcf7f9bf248203ff9f9507ca69ffad","tid":869380,"uid":4304,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T10:04:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">帳面仍賺308萬元</span>"},{"pid":"fc25fb3a3bdfb60392359badeb380977d20a2de0","tid":869380,"uid":21661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4961d52aa4fcf7f9bf248203ff9f9507ca69ffad","tid":869380,"uid":4304,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T10:04:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">帳面仍賺308萬元</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T10:14:15.000Z","msg":"都係唔計<br />\n唔